      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy test demonstrates convergence consistent with nominal scheme order for the primary QoI.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to the rotating-frame Navier-Stokes equations. Observed order of accuracy 1.92 (nominal: 2nd order). Residuals converged to 1e-6 for all continuity and momentum equations."
