      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed (4.2M, 12.1M, 31.8M cells). GCI on normalised hemolysis index: 2.7%. Richardson-extrapolated value used as reference. Production mesh is the 12.1M-cell configuration, balancing accuracy and computational cost."
