      "acceptanceCriteria": "The QoI (relative hemolysis index RH) is directly linked to the clinical decision criterion and is measurable in both simulation and reference data.",
      "rationale": "RH is the FDA-endorsed metric for comparative hemolysis assessment (FDA guidance 2021). The CFD post-processing pipeline computes RH via the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law model integrated along particle trajectories. The registry dataset records plasma-free haemoglobin enabling direct RH calculation. QoI alignment is confirmed."
    },
