      "rationale": "The observational registry enrolled patients undergoing adult cardiac surgery with the FDA generic centrifugal pump, matching the COU device geometry. Operating conditions span the COU envelope. Blood properties are representative of the target population. Validation activities are judged relevant to the COU at the required level."
